title: Havent gotten the teemoing icons yet
body: When are the icons supposed to come out exactly, since Ive seen a few people with the devil teemo icon or the pumpkin? I beat doombots and gifted someone during the first week of it, and they still havent come in. Thanks for the feedback when it comes{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}

replies.body: Some players may receive the icon before others, but our aim is to have it distributed to all eligible players by the 17th.  More details on that can also be found in the [teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page.  Hope that helps!
Thanks Porocles, i didnt have a chance to check that page out fully. It helped out a bunch on the icons
